&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Explore new directions and design patterns to meet the requirements while always pushing the quality of design forward&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
